<p class="note"><strong>Note:</strong> Configure <%= vars.product_short %> for high availability 
only after completing the <%= vars.product_short %> v1.7 upgrade.</p>

1. In the **<%= vars.product_tile %>** tile, click **Resource Config**.

1. To configure your control plane MySQL database for high availability, 
increase the **INSTANCES** value for **<%= vars.control_plane_db %>** to `3`.

1. To configure your control plane services, such as UAA and PKS CLI, for high availability, 
increase the **INSTANCES** value for **<%= vars.control_plane %>** to `2` or more.

1. Click **Save**.

1. Click **Apply Changes**.    
